{
    "text": "The Sirao Flower Gardens, more commonly referred to as Cebu\u2019s \u2018Mini-Amsterdam,\u2019 is one of the best attractions located in Cebu\u2019s Transcentral Highway that attracts tourists for its colorful fields of flowers. When the flower farm craze went viral on social media in 2015, hundreds of visitors flocked the barangay of Sirao to catch glimpse of the fiery multi-colored field of celosias \u2014 the main flower grown in Sirao Garden.   \ud83c\uddf5\ud83c\udded #discoverphilippines  Photographer : Unknown DM for Credits #sirao #flowers #philippines",
